{"tid":829212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔天降懷疑腐液 6男女受傷","createTime":"2018-09-20T09:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T11:20:11.000Z","uid":182758,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1de8a614718428e5f7454cb952f96ae4cf85520d","tid":829212,"uid":182758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"大埔發生天降懷疑腐液事件，多人受傷。下午4時許，廣福道96號大廈對開，有懷疑腐蝕性液體由高處墮下，大廈對開巴士站有3男3女走避不及被濺中，途人見狀報案。救護員接報趕至，替傷者初步處理傷口，再將6人送院治理。警方正封鎖現場登樓調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180920/58704134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180920%2F58704134&d=3wKPalFIRmNjt9PP99x%2B5fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=971e158a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180920%2F58704134&h=e9ca0862\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180920/58704134</a>"},{"pid":"8c4923fc9930040c482bcb7014f35d286eb709dd","tid":829212,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:11:41.000Z","msg":"十年後又來了"},{"pid":"cd25ffeb0fa9547dd0468995160f35b5decc2128","tid":829212,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T09:12:09.000Z","msg":"破案率最勁既香港警犬<br />\n10年前破到案未?"},{"pid":"02a112cd5e148a369d684f13a9baa6e8460d0cab","tid":829212,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T11:19:10.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"f7851201a872c2cc022dc5d96bf9b94d69fdeb19","tid":829212,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1322619/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1322619%2F&d=3wKPalFIRmNjt9PP99x%2B5fiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7b9fed24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1322619%2F&h=16bfb7fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1322619/</a><br />\n<br />\n大埔廣福道發生懷疑腐液從天而降事件，警方事後拘捕一名男子。<br />\n<br />\n事發下午3時33分，大埔廣福道96號一幢大廈2樓，一名男戶主使用通渠水通冷氣去水喉時，不慎將通渠水滴落地下。6名途人走避不及被濺中，包括一名11歲男童。途人報案。救護員接報到場，為其中5名傷者處理傷口後，無需送院，11歲男童則頸受傷，已送院進一步治療。警方正調查事件。"}]}